description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a bill that's intention to ban TikTok for "national security" is moving through incredibly fast. Is this bill touching the real root of the concern or is it just a way to allow a wave of censorship. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: The TikTok Ban Is Moving Forward...
